                However, Magic has limitations, including a lack of specialization in niche business areas and a workforce located in the Philippines, potentially leading to delays due to timezone differences. Moreover, their TrustPilot and Indeed reviews show mixed reactions from clients and assistant alike. These factors could make Magic less suitable for specialized or time-sensitive business requirements.
